# Claude Code local install artifacts. .claude/skills/ contains a mix
# of real directories (duplicates of files also tracked under
# .agents/skills/, .opencode/skills/, .github/skills/) and 6 symlinks
# (feature-sliced-design, grill-me, grill-with-docs,
# improve-codebase-architecture, to-issues, to-prd) that the installer
# creates locally. The symlinks can't be passed to prettier (it
# refuses to follow symlinks for security and aborts the whole
# lint-staged run), so they must never be staged. Listed by name to
# leave the real .claude/skills/ files unblocked.
.claude/skills/feature-sliced-design
.claude/skills/grill-me
.claude/skills/grill-with-docs
.claude/skills/improve-codebase-architecture
.claude/skills/to-issues
.claude/skills/to-prd

